ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectOrder Repealing Order in Council P.C. 1987-86 of January 22, 1987
PrecisOrder repealing Order in Council P.C. 1987-86 of January 22, 1987 which declared that certain section sections of the Financial Administration Act apply to Canada Lands Company (Mirabel) Limited, Canada Lands Company (Le Vieux-Port de Montréal) Limited and Canada Lands Compagny (Vieux-Port de Québec) Inc. as if they were parent Crown corporations set out in Part I of Schedule C of the Act.
